{
  "texts": [
    "Our target population encompassed researchers affiliated with diverse universities and academic institutions across Egypt.",
    "To ensure a representative and heterogeneous sample, we implemented a multi-pronged approach recruitment strategy to identify, then to contact potential participants.",
    "Leveraging Online Research Networks• Targeted Searches on Scholarly Platforms: We utilized keyword-based searches on Google Scholar, Microsoft Teams, and ResearchGate to identify researchers actively publishing in fields relevant to the study.",
    "We then filtered results based on institutional affiliation and research focus to curate a targeted pool of potential participants.",
    "• Professional Social Media Groups: We disseminated study invitations and concise descriptions within pertinent research discussion groups on platforms like Facebook and LinkedIn."
  ]
}